          "reviewBody": "The educational system followed in the scool is really good.  Kids are happy studying here.  Every subject is explained  giving good examples and showing practically.\n\nKids are encouraged to participate in extracurricular activities like,  music, dance, sports, yoga etc.  They make sure all the kids get equal opportunity in everything.\n\nInfrastructure of the school is also good.  So overall experience with this school is excellent.",
